responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "BD2145C54103FF20CB4BF7B0D2DB8972", "Dugal Blackwood is the youngest brother of one of our veteran guards, Sergeant Blackwood of Briarmoor Watch. He has reportedly been active as a highwayman and holds up in Nikka\'Brae ruins, a newly established bandit outpost.")
